Usage: editBumpConnectTargetConstraint [-help] {-bump <string> | -selected } {-instName <string> {[-toInstName <string>] [-pinName <string> {[-toPinName <string>] [{-portNum <integer> -toPortNum <integer>}]}]}}

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-bump <string>           # delete bump connect target constraint on specified
                         # bump (string list, required)
-instName <string>       # the instName to change in bump connect target
                         # constraint (string, required)
-pinName <string>        # the pin name to change in bump connect target
                         # constraint (string, optional)
-portNum <integer>       # the port number to change in bump connect target
                         # constraint (int, optional)
-selected                # delete bump connect target constraint on selected
                         # bumps (bool, required)
-toInstName <string>     # the instName to change to in bump connect target
                         # constraint (string, optional)
-toPinName <string>      # the pin name to change to in bump connect target
                         # constraint (string, optional)
-toPortNum <integer>     # the port number to change to in bump connect target
                         # constraint (int, optional)